---
title: Hearty Turkey Burger Noodle Soup with Onion & Parsley
description: Are you ready for the epic-level comforting mash-up of burgers and noodle soup? You’ll begin by caramelizing onion and browning beef and spices. Stir in crushed tomatoes and curly cavatappi pasta, then simmer until tender for a simple, hearty one-pot meal (and a breezy clean up!). A sprinkle of parsley on top adds a bright, herbaceous touch.
